categories.title: Mouse
categories.description: Logitech  Bluetooth Mouses are a compact lightweight wireless mouse that's comfortable to use on the go, at home or in office. It connects to computers and any other devices supporting Bluetooth wireless technology. That eliminates the unsightly clutter of wires.

categories.title: Keyboard
categories.description: Trusted legacy. Lasting durability. The keyboard features a solid aluminum build with expertly engineered Romer-GTM mechanical switches.

categories.title: Webcam
categories.description: For on-the-go professionals, Logitech HD Webcam makes it easy to bring a webcam to every meeting. The compact, folding design simplifies travel, and features a universal mounting clip for your laptop or other device. High-definition video presents clear images for every participant to see.

reviews.title: Nice Product and professional service
reviews.comment: I am pleases with Logitech for working in Pakistan. I just recently bought mouse, it is a nice wireless mouse and performing better than what I had from Dell last time.
